high_descs: Turn around right and go nearby to the microwave.
Pick the egg from the oven and close the oven door.
Take the pot, turn left and walk towards the bed room and go nearby to the bed.
Put the egg in the pot.
Pick the pot and ready to move.
Take the pan and move towards the hall and go nearby to the diningtable.
Place the pot in the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Pick an egg from the oven, put it inside the pot and place it on the dining table in the hall.

high_descs: Turn right to reach the microwave in the kitchen.
Pick up the egg from the microwave.
Turn around and head left and to reach the bedroom and walk to the bed.
Put the egg in the pot.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Turn around to reach the dining table on the left.
Put the pot on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the egg on the dining table.

high_descs: Walk ahead and right to go around the counters to the microwave in the corner of the room.
Pick up the egg on the left inside the microwave.
Walk back around the counters to exit the kitchen area, then left into the bedroom, approaching the pot on the middle of the bed.
Put the egg in the pot.
Pick up the pot.
Exit the room the way you came in, then turn left to the coffee table in front of the sofa.
Put the pot down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with an egg in it on a coffee table.
